		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="63" y="369" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="80" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="510" height="81" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="80" color="#ffffff">守望者·堕天</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="575" y="52" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="48" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="318" height="51" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="48" color="#ffffff">全技能一图流</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1128" width="442" height="174" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">监望之统摄：大招之前会施放2次，每次会分别记录<span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span>的攻击次数，首次施放时，当某一元素次数达</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3次</span><span>时，即为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">记录完成</span><span>，并作为元素星的属性储存；若第二次记录的元素与首次</span><span color="#ffdfbf">相同</span><span>，则需要</span><span color="#ffdfbf">9次攻击</span><span>才能被记录。<br/>元素星：生命值</span><span color="#ffdfbf">243740</span><span>(4.0F)，为守望者的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1/6</span><span>；活性免疫对应元素伤害，惰性具有高抗；深渊内，若为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">异色</span><span>元素星，则星星生命值降低至守望者的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1/15</span><span>。<br/><br/>部分技能期间，抗打断80。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="65" y="501" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffe599" width="474" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffe599">开眼者·世界望楼之守望</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="60" y="821" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="32" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="280" height="35" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="32" color="#ffffff">抗性数据(单位%)</p>
