		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者从门中扔下长矛进入战斗，造成<span color="#ffe599">20%</span><span>伤害，随后从门中出现。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者持矛立即进行破击，造成<span color="#ffe599">41%</span><span>伤害，随后翻身，驾驭着长矛继续冲击，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">47%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者抬起长矛，朝前方的地上猛击，造成<span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，守望者扔起长矛，纵身一跃，在玩家处落下，造成<span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者将长矛朝前方丢出，长矛经过将造成<span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="414" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者进行2段左右划攻击，依次造成<span color="#ffe599">32%,34%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="434" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者将长矛先转一圈，造成<span color="#ffe599">40%</span><span>伤害，随后立即进入</span><span textDecoration="underline">监望之统摄</span><span>状态，持续5s；记录完毕后/未成功记录 将造成</span><span color="#ffffbf">对应元素</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffe599">岩元素</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffbfbf">68%</span><span>伤害。累计施放2次后立即准备大招「现象之谵妄」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="1011" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">守望者移至场地中央，并进行蓄力，同时召唤2枚<span textDecoration="underline">元素星</span><span>，属性为先前两次所记录的元素，同时免疫对应元素伤害；</span><span color="#ffdfbf">难以破坏</span><span>的惰性岩元素星不免疫伤害，但具有高抗；<br/></span><span color="#ffdfbf">18s</span><span>后，将根据场上剩余的元素星，依次造成</span><span color="#ffffbf">对应元素</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffbfbf">100%</span><span>伤害。破坏第</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2</span><span>颗元素星将对守望者造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2段3%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2段9%生命值</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffffbf">对应元素真伤</span><span>(仅暴击的一段有附着)。<br/>深境螺旋内，若守望者召唤了</span><span color="#ffdfbf">不同的两枚元素星</span><span>，则它们的生命值将大幅下降。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
